<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Help Us | Jewelry Virtual Try-On</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylenew.css">
  <script src="scriptnew.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('header.ejs') %>
      <section class="help-us">
        <div class="help-us-container">
          <div class="help-us-text">
            <h2 class="support">SUPPORT</h2>
            <h1 class="faq-heading1 fqh">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h1>
            <p class="faq-description">Your guide to using the virtual try-on feature and getting the best experience with our jewelry.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="faq-section">
        <div class="faq-container">
          <!-- Left Section (Heading and Description) -->
          <div class="faq-left">
            <h2 class="faq-heading">General FAQs</h2>
            <p class="faq-paragraph">Your guide to understanding how our jewelry works, the virtual try-on feature, and everything else you need to know to have the best shopping experience with us.</p>
          </div>
      
          <!-- Right Section (Collapsible Questions and Answers) -->
          <div class="faq-right">
            <div class="faq-item">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                <p class="faq-text">How do I use the virtual try-on feature?</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>To use the virtual try-on feature, simply click on any piece of jewelry and choose the "Try On" option. You'll be able to see how the piece looks on you using augmented reality technology.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
            <div class="faq-item">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                <p class="faq-text">Can I return a product after using the virtual try-on?</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes, you can return the jewelry within 30 days of receiving it, even if you have used the virtual try-on feature. Please refer to our return policy for more details.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
            <div class="faq-item">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                <p class="faq-text">Is the virtual try-on feature available on all jewelry?</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Currently, the virtual try-on feature is available for most of our jewelry collection.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
            <div class="faq-item">
              <div class="faq-question">
                <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                <p class="faq-text">What are the system requirements for virtual try-on?</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>You need a laptop or desktop computer with a camera  support to use the virtual try-on feature. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="steps">
        <div class="steps-header">
          <h2>Steps to Try On</h2>
          <p>Follow these simple steps to try on our jewelry virtually and find the perfect match for you.</p>
        </div>
      
        <div class="steps-container">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">1</div>
            <div class="step-description">
              <h3>Step 1: Choose Your Jewelry</h3>
              <p>Browse through our stunning jewelry collection and choose the piece you'd like to try on.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">2</div>
            <div class="step-description">
              <h3>Step 2: Enable Your Camera</h3>
              <p>Enable your camera to allow the virtual try-on feature to work seamlessly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">3</div>
            <div class="step-description">
              <h3>Step 3: Adjust the Jewelry</h3>
              <p>Adjust the size and position of the jewelry to see how it looks on you in real-time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">4</div>
            <div class="step-description">
              <h3>Step 4: Make Your Decision</h3>
              <p>Get a clear view of how the jewelry looks on you and decide if it's the one!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="video-section">
        <div class="video-header">
          <h2>TUTORIAL</h2>
          <p>Watch this quick tutorial to understand how to use the virtual try-on feature and get the best experience with our jewelry.</p>
        </div>
      
        <div class="video-container">
          <!-- Video Tag for local video -->
          <video controls>
            <source src="images/demo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
          </video>
        </div>
        
      </section>
      <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
          
          <div class="footer-about">
            <h3>About Us</h3>
            <p>
              Adorn Ease offers a unique collection of exquisite jewelry,
              including earrings, glasses, and nosepins. Our mission is to bring
              elegance and beauty to your everyday life with high-quality pieces
              that suit every style and occasion.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-contact">
            <h3>Exclusively</h3>
            <p>
              Adorn Ease is your ultimate destination for a seamless virtual
              jewelry shopping experience. Explore a wide range of exquisite
              earrings, nosepins, noserings, and sunglasses, all crafted to
              enhance your style and confidence. With our innovative virtual
              try-on feature powered by advanced AR technology, you can
              visualize how each piece complements your look before making a
              purchase. 
            </p>
            
          </div>
          <div class="footer-links">
            <h3>Quick Links</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/AdornHomePage">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="Aboutus">About Us</a></li>
              <li><a href="/productspage">Collection</a></li>
              
              <li><a href="/Help">Help</a></li>
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
          <p>&copy; 2024 Adorn Ease. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
      </footer>
      
      























      <script>
        // Select all the FAQ questions
        const faqQuestions = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question');
      
        // Add event listener for each FAQ question
        faqQuestions.forEach((question) => {
          question.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const answer = question.nextElementSibling;
      
            // Toggle the answer visibility
            answer.style.display = answer.style.display === 'block' ? 'none' : 'block';
      
            // Toggle the icon (plus to minus)
            const icon = question.querySelector('.faq-icon');
            icon.textContent = icon.textContent === '+' ? 'âˆ’' : '+';
          });
        });
      </script>
      
      
      
  

     
</body>
</html>
